<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Nuevo contacto</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0f172a;font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;color:#0f172a;">
    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background:#0f172a;padding:32px 0;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="640" style="width:640px;max-width:640px;background:#0b1224;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:28px 32px 20px 32px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#06b6d4);color:#fff;">
                <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;">Quick Build · Contacto</p>
                <h1 style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2;">Nuevo mensaje recibido</h1>
                <p style="margin:8px 0 0;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">Alguien completó el formulario de contacto en el sitio público.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:28px 32px;background:#0f172a;color:#e2e8f0;">
                <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse;">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.15);">
                      <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#94a3b8;">Nombre</p>
                      <p style="margin:4px 0 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#f8fafc;"><%= @contact_message.name %></p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.15);">
                      <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#94a3b8;">Email</p>
                      <p style="margin:4px 0 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#f8fafc;"><%= @contact_message.email %></p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.15);">
                      <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#94a3b8;">WhatsApp / Teléfono</p>
                      <p style="margin:4px 0 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#f8fafc;"><%= @contact_message.phone.presence || "No especificado" %></p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.15);">
                      <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#94a3b8;">Empresa</p>
                      <p style="margin:4px 0 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#f8fafc;"><%= @contact_message.company.presence || "No especificada" %></p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:16px 0 4px 0;">
                      <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#94a3b8;">Mensaje</p>
                      <div style="padding:14px 16px;border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.25);border-radius:10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);color:#e2e8f0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
                        <%= simple_format(@contact_message.message) %>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <div style="margin-top:18px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.1);">
                  <p style="margin:0;color:#cbd5e1;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;">Sugerencia: podés responder directamente a este correo (reply-to del solicitante) o iniciar una conversación por WhatsApp con el número informado.</p>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:16px 32px;background:#0b1224;color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.08);">
                <p style="margin:0;">Quick Build · Plataforma de gestión para constructores</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
